'''布莱兹酮合成'''（Blaise ketone synthesis）指[[酰氯|酰氯]]与[[有机锌试剂|有机锌试剂]]作用得到[[酮|酮]]类。<ref>Blaise, E. E.; Koehler, A. ''Bull. Soc. Chim.'' '''1910''', ''7'', 215.</ref><ref>Blaise, E. E. ''Bull. Soc. Chim.'' '''1911''', ''9'', 1.</ref>

[[Image:Blaise_Ketone_Synthesis_Scheme.png|center]]

亦可以用[[有机铜试剂|有机铜试剂]]代替有机锌。<ref>Posner, G. H.; Whitten, C. E. ''[[Organic_Syntheses|Organic Syntheses]]'', Coll. Vol. 6, p.248 (1988); Vol. 55, p.122 (1976). ([http://www.orgsyn.org/orgsyn/prep.asp?prep=cv6p0248 Article] {{Wayback|url=http://www.orgsyn.org/orgsyn/prep.asp?prep=cv6p0248 |date=20110114211551 }})</ref><ref>Fujisawa, T.; Sato, T. ''[[Organic_Syntheses|Organic Syntheses]]'', Coll. Vol. 8, p.441 (1993); Vol. 66, p.116 (1988). ([http://www.orgsyn.org/orgsyn/prep.asp?prep=cv8p0441 Article] {{Wayback|url=http://www.orgsyn.org/orgsyn/prep.asp?prep=cv8p0441 |date=20110514024652 }})</ref>

反应综述：<ref>Cason, J. ''[[Chem._Rev.|Chem. Rev.]]'' '''1947''', ''40'', 17.（综述）</ref><ref>Shirley, D. A. ''Org. React.'' '''1954''', ''8'', 29.（综述）</ref>

==变体==
===布莱兹-梅尔反应===
用β-[[羟基|羟基]]酰氯作为底物，生成β-[[羟基酮|羟基酮]]，进一步用[[硫酸|硫酸]]处理得到[[α,β-不饱和羰基化合物|α,β-不饱和酮]]。<ref>Blaise, E. E.; Maire, M. ''Compt. Rend.'' '''1907''', ''145'', 73.</ref>

